trans-unit.source: Acts as the top of a two-level named hierarchy of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection"></xref> collections.
trans-unit.target: Atua como a parte superior de uma hierarquia de dois níveis nomeada de <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection"> </xref> coleções.

trans-unit.source: The RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection class is both a root-level <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collection and a container for a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: A classe RootProfilePropertySettingsCollection é ambos um nível raiz <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>coleção e um contêiner para um <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection>coleção.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGroupSettingsCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>

trans-unit.source: These collections allow you to create named groups of more <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection> collections, each containing individual named <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> objects.
trans-unit.target: Essas coleções permitem que você crie grupos de mais nomeados <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>coleções, cada indivíduo recipiente nomeado <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings>objetos.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettingsCollection>
